text: Nseluka is a small town in northern Zambia. == Statistics == * elevation – == Transport == It has a station on the TAZARA railway. It is the proposed junction for a branch railway to Mpulungu on the shores of Lake Tanganyika.Railways Africa - EXTENDING BEYOND CHIPATA == See also == * Transport in Zambia == References == Category:Populated places in Zambia
